DESCRIPTION


Add the following to your RT config file:

Set($StrictLinkACL, 0);

@MailPlugins = qw(Auth::MailFrom Filter::SplitNotOpen);


Add the following lines to your autoreply message:


If this message is in reply to a previously submitted ticket, it's 
possible that ticket has been marked as closed. As we review this ticket,
we will also review previous correspondence and take apropriate action.

